const signatureProvider = new JsSignatureProvider([defaultPrivateKey]);
```

### JSON-RPC

Open a connection to JSON-RPC, include `fetch` when on NodeJS.
```js
const rpc = new JsonRpc('http://127.0.0.1:8888', { fetch });
```

